<p><a name="Articles" id="Articles"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Anti-psychiatry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: Articles">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Articles</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.oikos.org/antipsicen.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.oikos.org/antipsicen.htm" rel="nofollow">Oikos.org</a> - The Dark Side of Psychiatry</li>
<li><a href="http://medicine.plosjournals.org/perlserv?request=get-document&amp;doi=10.1371/journal.pmed.0020124" class="external text" title="http://medicine.plosjournals.org/perlserv?request=get-document&amp;doi=10.1371/journal.pmed.0020124" rel="nofollow">PLoS Medicine</a> - Why Most Published Research Findings Are False, by John P. A. Ioannidis. Vol. 2, No. 8, DOI:10.1371/journal.pmed.0020124.Last accessed 16 June 2006</li>
