</ul>
<p><a name="Organizations_critical_of_psychiatry" id="Organizations_critical_of_psychiatry"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Anti-psychiatry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Organizations critical of psychiatry">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Organizations critical of psychiatry</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.cchr.org" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.cchr.org" rel="nofollow">[3]</a> - Citizen's Commission on Human Rights</li>
<li><a href="http://laingsociety.org" class="external text" title="http://laingsociety.org" rel="nofollow">LaingSociety.org</a> - The Society for Laingian Studies, R.D. Laing (1927-1989)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.moshersoteria.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.moshersoteria.com/" rel="nofollow">Mosher Soteria</a> - <a href="/wiki/Loren_Mosher" title="Loren Mosher">Loren Mosher</a>, MD, (1933-2004)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.szasz.com" class="external text" title="http://www.szasz.com" rel="nofollow">Szasz.com</a> - The Thomas S. Szasz, MD, Cybercenter for Liberty and Responsibility</li>
<li><a href="http://www.icspp.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.icspp.org/" rel="nofollow">ICSPP.org</a> - International Center for the Study of Psychiatry and Psychology</li>
<li><a href="http://www.mindfreedom.org" class="external text" title="http://www.mindfreedom.org" rel="nofollow">MindFreedom.org</a> - Support Coalition International (a coalition of groups supporting "United Action for Human Rights in Mental Health")</li>
<li><a href="http://psychrights.org/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://psychrights.org/index.htm" rel="nofollow">PsychRights.org</a> - Law Project for Psychiatric Rights</li>
<li><a href="http://www.iaapa.ch/" class="external text" title="http://www.iaapa.ch/" rel="nofollow">IAAPA</a> International Association Against Psychiatric Assault</li>
<li><a href="http://www.psychiatricsurvivorarchives.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.psychiatricsurvivorarchives.com/" rel="nofollow">PSAT</a> Psychiatric Survivor Archives of Toronto</li>
<li><a href="http://tanadineen.com" class="external text" title="http://tanadineen.com" rel="nofollow">TanaDineen.com</a> Homepage of Tana Dineen</li>
<li><a href="http://community.livejournal.com/antipsychiatry/" class="external text" title="http://community.livejournal.com/antipsychiatry/" rel="nofollow">Anti-Psychiatry Livejournal</a> - Anti-Psychiatry Community on Livejournal, Most Updated Resource.</li>
</ul>
